  "texts": [
    "It conveys not only information but also experience and emotion.",
    "So far, AI has not been learned to generate truly emotional text as humans perceive it due to context variations and database limitations.",
    "However, as the technology evolves, we expect existing features to improve and new opportunities to emerge.",
    "XLinguae, Volume 17 Issue 1, January 2024, ISSN 1337-8384, eISSN 2453-711X"
  ]
}